##  Bot to upload images to imgbb.com and save the URL in a CSV file.
## Installation

clone  repo

```bash
git git@github.com:Taoista/upload_imgbb2023.git
```
enter the project
```bash
cd upload_imgbb2023
```

Recommendation (install virtualenv optional)
```bash
pip install virtualenv
```
Install package
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
copy .env.example to .env
```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

## Program Usage
```bash
python main.py
```
## Execution Blocks

> You can create the 'images' folder and place the images to be uploaded inside.
>>"In the .env file, there should be a variable named AI_IMGBB=, where you should enter your API key to be able to upload the images.


FOLDER .env
```
size image inf file .env
```
API_IMGBB=your_api_key
